Rihanna, 34, gave her fans a glimpse into her Super Bowl performance this Sunday as she took to the stage at the press conference. The singer stunned in a double-slit snakeskin printed skirt as she took to the stage to discuss her upcoming performance. She paired her revealing skirt with a fur-lined leather jacket that hung off one of her shoulders, with a low-cut top underneath. For her footwear, she matched her skirt with a pair of snakeskin patterned heels with straps that exposed her legs. She accessorised with large silver earrings, a choker and several rings while going for a bronzed makeup look.